{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM05_ST4_520.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x22,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x7e,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Why are slags coming from the ruin?<CR>What was the town watch doing!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f8,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Sorry. The slags have been restless lately."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f9,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Plus, part of the wall collapsed. They continue to emerge from the ruin, going on a rampage."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x7f,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "But still, what were those guys doing while these things were pouring out of the ruin!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1fa,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Well..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f8,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Sorry, kiddo. Our town watch is unreliable..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x194,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "No, don't worry about it.<CR>(It might actually be all my fault...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "(What should I do...?<CR>It's probably because of the<CR>Flower Crystal's influence...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, rampaging slags... So, slags can understand those \"words,\" as well..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Mr. Keith...when did you get here?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Just now. Something interesting seemed to be happening over here, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "The \"words\" the crystal emits must be like their god's voice, giving these slags their absolute orders."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "However, when you used it, the words were simply scattered without holding any meaning."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "The nonsensical voice of their god resounded within them. They seem to be deeply confused."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "What should I do...? If anyone gets injured, I'll‐"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I'm sure the people who live around here are used to this level of strife, so there's no need to worry."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x218,
            "name_id": 0x2f,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Boss! The big one that was inside started moving!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x205,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Whoa, whoa, he's gonna start moving, too...? Oh, this is...gonna be trouble."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x218,
            "name_id": 0x2f,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "On top of that, there's a girl floating in the air, giving the slags orders."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x218,
            "name_id": 0x2f,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "What the hell is going on...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Excuse me, but what did this girl look like?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x218,
            "name_id": 0x2f,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Well, her hair was short and...<CR>Huh? She kinda reminds me of you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "(So this girl... Is she Nio...?)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Boss, I'm gonna go."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f8,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "You? No way. It's too dangerous to go inside!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x196,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "No...I'm gonna go. I have to!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f9,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "If something happens, we won't be able to save you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Don't worry, this little darling will be fine. Let her go."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1fe,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "If you say so... But, if you feel like you're in danger, come back immediately!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Okay, it's decided then. Go."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Yes, sir! It's my fault, so I need to do something about it...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "Well, you don't have to get so worked up. If push comes to shove, I'll settle this."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "Above all else, with all this confusion, I'm sure there'll be moments you can catch them with their guard down."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "O-Okay...I'll get going!"
        }
    ]
}